Package: tidyclm
Title: Provides Methods for Functions in the \code{broom} Package for \code{clm} Objects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Barron",
                  email = "dnbarron@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides methods for the \code{tidy}, \code{tidy.summary}, 
    and \code{glance} generics in the \code{broom} package.  It also provides functions to
    obtain standard errors when data are clustered.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
